-- 2010-10-08T09:16:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-08/solarfun-says-hanwha-buys-stake-owns-almost-half-of-panel-maker.html
Solarfun Power Holdings Co., the
third-best performing panel maker this year on the Bloomberg
solar index, said Hanwha Chemical Corp. now owns almost half of
the Chinese solar-panel maker after buying stock.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeremy Van Loon in Berlin at 
